@node "Bugs" "Bug reports"
@next "Author"
@prev "License"
If you find something which you consider as an obvious bug or misfeature
please send me a bug report!

@{i}Try to be as detailed as possible and include a description about
your current setup.@{ui}

Please include the following information when sending me a bugreport:
 · Model
 · OS, WB and ppc.library version
 · List of patches

My address can be found in the @{"author section" link "Author" 0}.

